\fs40 \cf0 Updating
\fs24 \
\
\pard\pardeftab560
\cf0 First close any open instance of SamplerCentral.\
\
1. unzip and move the newer version folder of SamplerCentral 2.x.x to Applications\
2. Open the 
\f0\b new version
\f1\b0  of SamplerCentral\
3. Click 
\f0\b global setup
\f1\b0  from the menu and then the 
\f0\b update/merge
\f1\b0  button.\
4. Drag the 
\f0\b old version
\f1\b0  of SamplerCentral (the app) into the square that says 
\f0\b drop app here
\f1\b0 .\
5. Click the 
\f0\b reset/clean up
\f1\b0  button, click 
\f0\b ok
\f1\b0  in the pop up window\
6. Click the 
\f0\b merge from old
\f1\b0  button, click 
\f0\b ok
\f1\b0  in the pop up window\
7. Close and open SamplerCentral again (or press 
\f0\b cmd+k
\f1\b0 , this restarts the app)\
8. If it all seems to work fine remember to also remove the SamplerCentral icon from the dock of the old version and drag the new version of the app to the dock.\
\
